{"tid":2456684,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"我不會忘記，在香港人有需要時，張俊傑兩脅插刀。","createTime":"2021-03-22T06:18:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T11:51:30.000Z","uid":343520,"like":53,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1d34e3ab663a114a89b0088e72f8f55d1de8ece2","tid":2456684,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T06:18:24.000Z","msg":"我不會忘記，在香港人有需要時，張俊傑兩脅插刀。<br />\n<br />\n高度的執行力、迅速的決策、秉持初心的付出與參與。<br />\n<br />\n幫醫護、幫學生、派飯給長者，以及他以自己能力，提供更多就業機會予同路人。<br />\n<br />\n之後，他頭上是刀，腹背也是刀，不斷被製造話題與問題。<br />\n<br />\n受外界言論影響，經常令他意志消沉，但他又絕不容易被打沉。<br />\n<br />\n晚上見張俊傑，他多數很愁。但是，翌日他又會清晨跑步，整理思緒，餘下的時間，只見他努力找方法解決問題 - 積極地，不抱怨，不放負，不追究，不記仇，把一切孭上身。<br />\n<br />\n在「解決自己問題」和「製造別人問題」兩類人之間，我永遠覺得前者更值得尊重。<br />\n<br />\n我尊重和重視這位朋友，張俊傑加油、龍門加油！<br />\n<br />\n張俊傑 龍門冰室/瓏門冰室<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KN4FLHm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKN4FLHm.jpg&h=9fa4c853&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e415501febc7c9fcdf8c12d874be5770fb050dc5","tid":2456684,"uid":372210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T06:18:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b111beaaa5b8cd622048c12431186cd5dc5641ac","tid":2456684,"uid":13395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T06:20:07.000Z","msg":"張生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"697d2456b7ad755cd7bfb89db8b871c677f54d0c","tid":2456684,"uid":58201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T06:20:22.000Z","msg":"咸能4"},{"pid":"7c2feb6676425b2ee8c81f291c4420c64d0ceaae","tid":2456684,"uid":367153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T06:21:24.000Z","msg":"樓主少數認真po<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7fe0010b1f9fcd9becfa63ab2b